n class=\"mntl-author-tooltip__learn-more-text\">Learn about Serious Eats'</span>\n<a\nhref=\"/about-us-5120006#toc-editorial-guidelines\"\nrel=\"nocaes\"\nclass=\"mntl-author-tooltip__learn-more-link\"\n>Editorial Process</a>\n</div>\n</div></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"mntl-attribution__item-date\">Updated August 10, 2018</div></div>\n</div></div></div>\n</div><div class=\"loc article-content\"><div id=\"article__broad-video-jw_1-0\" class=\"comp article__broad-video-jw mntl-jwplayer-broad mntl-block is-hidden\" data-pixel-depth=\"100\"><div id=\"mntl-jwplayer-broad__video_1-0\" class=\"comp mntl-jwplayer-broad__video mntl-jwplayer mm-video lazyload\" data-bgset data-sizes=\"auto\"></div>\n<div id=\"mntl-jwplayer-broad__title_1-0\" class=\"comp mntl-jwplayer-broad__title mntl-block\"><div id=\"mntl-jwplayer-broad__title--text_1-0\" class=\"comp mntl-jwplayer-broad__title--text mntl-text-block text-utility-100\"></div>\n<button id=\"mntl-jwplayer-broad__title-icon--close_1-0\" class=\"comp mntl-jwplayer-broad__title-icon--close mntl-block text-label-100\" data-click-tracked=\"false\"><span id=\"mntl-text-block_3-0\" class=\"comp mntl-text-block\">Close</span>\n<svg class=\"icon close-icon \"\n>\n<use xmlns:xlink=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink\" xlink:href=\"#close-icon\" href=\"#close-icon\"></use>\n</svg></button></div></div>\n<div id=\"figure-wrapper--article__container_1-0\" class=\"comp figure-wrapper--article__container mntl-block\"><figure id=\"primary-image_1-0\" class=\"comp primary-image mntl-universal-primary-image primary-image\"> <div class=\"primary-image__media\">\n<div class=\"img-placeholder\" style=\"padding-bottom:75.0%;\">\n<img\nsrc=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/W7Pm8hPSNVbRnM_-4n0ybP4O088=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2016__05__20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2-c15d2e980b234ce4b1c73ade0eec31bb.jpg\"\nwidth=\"1500\"\nheight=\"1125\"\nsrcset=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/K8JHvcT8ooqsDlNR75r3xTAtrEo=/750x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2016__05__20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2-c15d2e980b234ce4b1c73ade0eec31bb.jpg 750w\"\nsizes=\"750px\"\nalt=\"20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2.jpg\"\nclass=\" primary-image__image mntl-primary-image--blurry\"\nonload=\"(function(e){e.classList.add(&#39;loaded&#39;)})(this)\"\nstyle=\"--blurry: url(&#39;data:image/gif;charset=utf-8;base64,&#39;)\"\n/>\n<noscript>\n<img\nsrc=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/W7Pm8hPSNVbRnM_-4n0ybP4O088=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2016__05__20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2-c15d2e980b234ce4b1c73ade0eec31bb.jpg\"\nwidth=\"1500\"\nheight=\"1125\"\nclass=\"loaded primary-img--noscript primary-image__image mntl-primary-image--blurry\"\nsrcset=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/K8JHvcT8ooqsDlNR75r3xTAtrEo=/750x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2016__05__20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2-c15d2e980b234ce4b1c73ade0eec31bb.jpg 750w\"\nsizes=\"750px\"\nalt=\"20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2.jpg\"\n/>\n</noscript>\n</div> </div>\n</figure></div>\n<div id=\"article-content-container_1-0\" class=\"comp article-content-container mntl-block\"><div id=\"mntl-sc-page_1-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-page mntl-block structured-content text-passage\" data-sc-sticky-offset=\"100\" data-sc-ad-label-height=\"11\" data-sc-ad-track-spacing=\"100\" data-sc-min-track-height=\"250\" data-sc-max-track-height=\"600\" data-sc-breakpoint=\"50em\" data-sc-load-immediate=\"5\" data-sc-content-positions=\"[1, 1, 1, 1250, 1, 1, 1, 1]\" data-bind-scroll-on-start=\"true\"><p id=\"mntl-sc-block_1-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"> I know you get that feeling, because I get it, too. It&#39;s the feeling that comes on around 5:30 in the evening. You realize that dinnertime is rolling up, and you&#39;ve been putting off deciding what to make all day. It&#39;s starting to get a little late to put real effort into anything, and you&#39;re panicking a bit. Maybe you poke at your favorite websites for some inspiration. Or maybe you try to get all tech-savvy and say, &#34;Alexa, what should I make for dinner?&#34;*\n</p>\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_2-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\"></div>\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_3-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"> Her answer is <em>always</em> &#34;Pizza is a good choice, but don&#39;t forget your vegetables&#34; or &#34;I suggest something healthy and delicious.&#34; Gee, thanks, Alexa.\n</p>\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_4-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\"></div>\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_5-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"> It&#39;s nights like these that I&#39;m particularly happy that springtime makes it so darn easy to be lazy. So much green spring produce is in the supermarket and farmers market, and, best of all, that spring produce actually <em>benefits</em> from lazy cooking. Generally, the less you do to it, the better.\n</p>\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_6-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\"></div>\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_7-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"> For this simple, light supper, I barely do anything to the fava beans and carrots.\n</p>\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_8-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\"></div>\n<figure id=\"mntl-sc-block_9-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block lifestyle-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-image--no-theme no-theme figure-landscape figure-high-res\"> <div class=\"figure-media\">\n<div class=\"img-placeholder\" style=\"padding-bottom:75.0%;\">\n<img\ndata-src=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/A-4zABcFqJ4C35RPJugHMtWu29w=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2015__05__20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce06-081c7646fa824a1cac106d9f3c3ab54d.jpg\"\nwidth=\"1500\"\nheight=\"1125\"\ndata-srcset=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/y7rTkAvro8UHjFxNy5yew7fDFlQ=/750x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2015__05__20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce06-081c7646fa824a1cac106d9f3c3ab54d.jpg 750w\"\ndata-sizes=\"750px\"\nalt=\"20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce06.jpg\"\nclass=\"lazyload mntl-image mntl-image universal-image__image\"\ndata-expand=\"300\"\ndata-hi-res-src=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/A-4zABcFqJ4C35RPJugHMtWu29w=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2015__05__20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce06-081c7646fa824a1cac106d9f3c3ab54d.jpg\"\nid=mntl-sc-block-image_1-0\ndata-tracking-container=\"true\"\ndata-img-lightbox=\"true\"\ndata-click-tracked=\"true\"\n/>\n<noscript>\n<img\nsrc=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/A-4zABcFqJ4C35RPJugHMtWu29w=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2015__05__20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce06-081c7646fa824a1cac106d9f3c3ab54d.jpg\"\nwidth=\"1500\"\nheight=\"1125\"\nclass=\"img--noscript mntl-image mntl-image universal-image__image\"\nsrcset=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/y7rTkAvro8UHjFxNy5yew7fDFlQ=/750x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2015__05__20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce06-081c7646fa824a1cac106d9f3c3ab54d.jpg 750w\"\nsizes=\"750px\"\nalt=\"20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce06.jpg\"\n/>\n</noscript>\n</div> </div>\n</figure>\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_10-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"> For the favas, I start by popping them out of their pods, then I blanch them in boiling water for just about a minute before shocking them in ice water. (Check out my <a href=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/food-lab-spring-produce-how-to-blanch\" data-component=\"link\" data-source=\"inlineLink\" data-type=\"internalLink\" data-ordinal=\"1\">guide to blanching spring vegetables for more details</a>.)\n</p>\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_11-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\"></div>\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_12-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"> Fava beans have a skin around each bean that becomes far easier to remove after they&#39;ve been blanched; a little squeeze should pop them right out of it. There&#39;s another good reason to blanch with the skin still on:\n</p>\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_13-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\"></div>\n<figure id=\"mntl-sc-block_14-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block lifestyle-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-image--no-theme no-theme figure-landscape figure-high-res\"> <div class=\"figure-media\">\n<div class=\"img-placeholder\" style=\"padding-bottom:75.0%;\">\n<img\ndata-src=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/uNnDRXPGDQ-dxDz-MB1xcZpiFoE=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2015__05__20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce01-d0dc7276bc484500acd1240f44a2674a.jpg\"\nwidth=\"1500\"\nheight=\"1125\"\ndata-srcset=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/Tiyj85_Emd8s9Zsp4DK2iiKNxW0=/750x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2015__05__20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce01-d0dc7276bc484500acd1240f44a2674a.jpg 750w\"\ndata-sizes=\"750px\"\nalt=\"20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce01.jpg\"\nclass=\"lazyload mntl-image mntl-image universal-image__image\"\ndata-expand=\"300\"\ndata-hi-res-src=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/uNnDRXPGDQ-dxDz-MB1xcZpiFoE=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2015__05__20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce01-d0dc7276bc484500acd1240f44a2674a.jpg\"\nid=mntl-sc-block-image_2-0\ndata-tracking-container=\"true\"\ndata-img-lightbox=\"true\"\ndata-click-tracked=\"true\"\n/>\n<noscript>\n<img\nsrc=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/uNnDRXPGDQ-dxDz-MB1xcZpiFoE=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2015__05__20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce01-d0dc7276bc484500acd1240f44a2674a.jpg\"\nwidth=\"1500\"\nheight=\"1125\"\nclass=\"img--noscript mntl-image mntl-image universal-image__image\"\nsrcset=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/Tiyj85_Emd8s9Zsp4DK2iiKNxW0=/750x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2015__05__20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce01-d0dc7276bc484500acd1240f44a2674a.jpg 750w\"\nsizes=\"750px\"\nalt=\"20150504-how-to-prepare-spring-green-produce01.jpg\"\n/>\n</noscript>\n</div> </div>\n</figure>\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_15-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"> The bright green bean on the right was blanched in the skin, while the pale bean on the left was blanched out of its skin. Not only does that emerald-green color look better, but beans blanched in the skin also taste better.\n</p>\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_16-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\"></div>\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_17-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"> I thinly slice the carrots with a very sharp, thin knife (you can use a vegetable peeler or a <a href=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/what-are-the-best-cheap-mandoline-vegetable-fruit-slicers\" data-component=\"link\" data-source=\"inlineLink\" data-type=\"internalLink\" data-ordinal=\"1\">mandoline</a> if you'd like), dropping them straight into the same ice bath as the favas, which helps the uncooked carrots curl nicely and gives them a crisper texture. After draining, I toss both with some extra-virgin olive oil, lemon juice, lemon zest, and a thinly sliced shallot. If the carrots have attractive tender greens, you can add those, too.\n</p>\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_18-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\"></div>\n<figure id=\"mntl-sc-block_19-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block lifestyle-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-image mntl-sc-block-image--no-theme no-theme figure-landscape figure-high-res\"> <div class=\"figure-media\">\n<div class=\"img-placeholder\" style=\"padding-bottom:75.0%;\">\n<img\ndata-src=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/W7Pm8hPSNVbRnM_-4n0ybP4O088=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2016__05__20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2-c15d2e980b234ce4b1c73ade0eec31bb.jpg\"\nwidth=\"1500\"\nheight=\"1125\"\ndata-srcset=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/K8JHvcT8ooqsDlNR75r3xTAtrEo=/750x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2016__05__20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2-c15d2e980b234ce4b1c73ade0eec31bb.jpg 750w\"\ndata-sizes=\"750px\"\nalt=\"20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2.jpg\"\nclass=\"lazyload mntl-image mntl-image universal-image__image\"\ndata-expand=\"300\"\ndata-hi-res-src=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/W7Pm8hPSNVbRnM_-4n0ybP4O088=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2016__05__20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2-c15d2e980b234ce4b1c73ade0eec31bb.jpg\"\nid=mntl-sc-block-image_3-0\ndata-tracking-container=\"true\"\ndata-img-lightbox=\"true\"\ndata-click-tracked=\"true\"\n/>\n<noscript>\n<img\nsrc=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/W7Pm8hPSNVbRnM_-4n0ybP4O088=/1500x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2016__05__20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2-c15d2e980b234ce4b1c73ade0eec31bb.jpg\"\nwidth=\"1500\"\nheight=\"1125\"\nclass=\"img--noscript mntl-image mntl-image universal-image__image\"\nsrcset=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/thmb/K8JHvcT8ooqsDlNR75r3xTAtrEo=/750x0/filters:no_upscale():max_bytes(150000):strip_icc()/__opt__aboutcom__coeus__resources__content_migration__serious_eats__seriouseats.com__images__2016__05__20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2-c15d2e980b234ce4b1c73ade0eec31bb.jpg 750w\"\nsizes=\"750px\"\nalt=\"20160503-fava-carrot-ricotta-salad-recipe-2.jpg\"\n/>\n</noscript>\n</div> </div>\n</figure>\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_20-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"> To turn this from a side salad into a light lunch or supper, I serve it all on top of a healthy dollop of good-quality ricotta cheese, along with some slices of hearty toast drizzled with olive oil.\n</p>\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_21-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\"></div>\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_22-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"> Dinner&#39;s ready, and it&#39;s only 5:45. <em>Now</em> what am I going to do for the next hour?\n</p>\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_23-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\"></div>\n<p id=\"mntl-sc-block_24-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-html\"> &#34;Alexa, play me some karaoke!&#34;\n</p>\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_25-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block mntl-sc-block-adslot mntl-block\"></div>\n<div id=\"mntl-sc-block_26-0\" class=\"comp mntl-sc-block lifestyle-sc-block-featuredlink mntl-sc-block-featuredlink mntl-block getrecipe-link\"><a\nhref=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/easy-fava-bean-carrot-salad-recipe\"\nrel=\"nocaes\"\nid=\"mntl-sc-block-featuredlink__link_1-0\"\nclass=\"mntl-sc-block-featuredlink__link mntl-text-link \"\ndata-tracking-container=\"true\"\ndata-tracking-id=\"featured-link-getrecipe\"\n><span class=\"link__wrapper\">Easy Fava Bean and Carrot Salad With Ricotta Recipe</span></a>\n<div id=\"getrecipe-container_1-0\" class=\"comp getrecipe-container mntl-block getrecipe__header\"></div></div></div>\n<div id=\"sources_1-0\" class=\"comp sources mntl-block\"></div>\n<div id=\"lifestyle-food-breadcrumbs--chips_1-0\" class=\"comp lifestyle-food-breadcrumbs--chips mntl-universal-breadcrumbs--chips mntl-block\"><div id=\"mntl-breadcrumbs__read-more_1-0\" class=\"comp mntl-breadcrumbs__read-more mntl-text-block text-title-100\">Explore more:</div>\n<ul id=\"mntl-universal-breadcrumbs_1-0\" class=\"comp mntl-universal-breadcrumbs mntl-block text-label-300 breadcrumbs\" data-tracking-container=\"true\"><li id=\"mntl-breadcrumbs__item_1-0\" class=\"comp mntl-breadcrumbs__item mntl-block\"><a\nhref=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/all-recipes-5117985\"\nrel=\"nocaes\"\nclass=\"mntl-text-link mntl-breadcrumbs__link\"\nid=\"mntl-text-link_4-0\"\ndata-tracking-container=\"true\"\n><span class=\"link__wrapper\">Recipes</span></a></li>\n<li id=\"mntl-breadcrumbs__item_2-0\" class=\"comp mntl-breadcrumbs__item mntl-block\"><a\nhref=\"https://www.seriouseats.com/recipes-by-course-5117906\"\nrel=\"nocaes\"\nclass=\"mntl-text-link mntl-breadcrumbs__link\"\nid=\"mn